Society also tells me that killing the guy in his mercedes so I can have a better car is wrong.<br>
<br>
Basically, a civilization gets along because of a common social contract instituted as customs and laws.  Part of what is customary is a uniform language.  Many of the racial issues that occur between peoples occurs due to language barriers and things that promote these barriers actually worsen instability in mixed cultures.<br>
<br>
On a strictly personal level, when I see someone talking in this manner, I react in exactly the same way I would in EQ if someone came up and said "d00d gimme sow plz kthx"  People might think that is racist, but it isn't.  There are enough white suburban wanna-be gang bangers out there that talk like this to make it an equal opportunity annoyance. <p><SELECT NAME="D1">
